OL,3,CBoy who attacked girl with sword on
OL,4,Ccamping trip: 'I'm a monster'
OL,6,FA boy who attacked a girl with a sword
OL,7,Fon a camping trip has described
OL,8,Fhimself as a "monster" but denied
OL,9,Fintending to kill her.
OL,11,FThe 15-year-old is on trial at Hull
OL,12,FCrown Court accused of the attempted
OL,13,Fmurder of a 13-year-old girl in an
OL,14,Fincident on 1 November last year.
OL,16,FShe was stabbed 10 times with a weapon
OL,17,Fsimilar to a Samurai sword after a
OL,18,Fgroup of friends went camping off the
OL,19,FA63 near Hessle, outside Hull.
