OL,3,CBoy who attacked girl with sword on
OL,4,Ccamping trip: 'I'm a monster'
OL,6,FGiving evidence on Friday, the boy,
OL,7,Fwho was 14 at the time of thecannot be
OL,8,Fnamed because of his age, said he
OL,9,F"just wanted to hurt" the girl.
OL,11,FHe said he had been told to "hurt her"
OL,12,Fby another girl in the group of seven
OL,13,Fafter a disagreement.
OL,15,FAsked by defence barrister David
OL,16,FGodfrey why he stopped the attack, the
OL,17,Fboy replied: "Because I felt too bad,
OL,18,FI'm a monster."
OL,20,FHe said he "went back to the tent and
OL,21,Fcried" after the attack.
