OL,3,CBoy who attacked girl with sword on
OL,4,Ccamping trip: 'I'm a monster'
OL,6,FThe court has heard how the girl
OL,7,Fsuffered injuries to her head, neck,
OL,8,Fchest, back and arms as well as damage
OL,9,Fto her lung and liver. She was found
OL,10,Fcovered in blood by passing drivers
OL,11,Fafter staggering on to the road.
OL,13,FThe boy has already admitted wounding
OL,14,Fwith intent and possession of a sword,
OL,15,Fbut denies attempted murder.
OL,17,FDuring 90 minutes of evidence, he
OL,18,Fspoke of how he held the girl's
OL,19,Fshoulder to the ground because "it
OL,20,Fwould be easier to stab her".
