OL,3,CBoy who attacked girl with sword on
OL,4,Ccamping trip: 'I'm a monster'
OL,6,FHe told the girl: "I'm sorry."
OL,8,FThe boy said he felt "disgusted" at
OL,9,Fwhat he done and stopped attacking the
OL,10,Fgirl because he "felt so bad".
OL,12,FAsked if he wanted to kill her he
OL,13,Fsaid: "That was not my intention."
OL,15,FProsecutor David Lamb KC asked the boy
OL,16,Fwhy he had left the victim alone in
OL,17,Fwoodland and had not tried to get help.
OL,19,FHe replied: "I don't know."
