OL,6,FAsked by the barrister why he lied to
OL,7,Fthe police about not attacking the
OL,8,Fgirl, he said: "I knew I had hurt her,
OL,9,FI was scared."
OL,11,FThe court also heard details of a
OL,12,Fletter from the boy's grandparents
OL,13,Fdescribing him as having "always shown
OL,14,Fempathy" and being "bright and well
OL,15,Fmannered".
OL,17,FThe trial continues.
